        "q": "What does \"one session\" actually mean?",
        "a": "You sign in once; mail, storage, auth and every other product see the same session. No separate account, password or tab per product."
      },
      "alacarte": {
        "q": "Can I use the products individually?",
        "a": "Yes. Open only what you need; the rest of the dock stays put. Adding another one later is a single click."
      },
      "sdk": {
        "q": "Is there an API and SDK?",
        "a": "Yes. One access token covers the TypeScript, Python, Go and PHP SDKs — or plain REST. Start with npm i @sentroy-co/client-sdk."
      },
      "free": {
        "q": "Can I start for free?",
        "a": "Yes, and nobody asks for a credit card. Upgrade as you grow; pricing is right above, no surprises."
      },
      "data": {
        "q": "Is my data safe?",
        "a": "We run our own company on this platform every day. Access is scoped per company, and every critical action lands in the audit log."
      }
